NUMBER 641
NAME Enshrouded in Smoke
*DESCRIPTION_START
You cough and gag as the cloud of noxious smoke invades your throat and lungs.
The area about you has become entirely obscured and your stinging eyes offer
no help. The wind does, however, seem to be blowing the smoke away.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ASTRAL
CALL 33
OUTOFBODY

IFVAR ORG = 13
  ECHO PLAYER Having practiced maneuvering about in the smoke cloud, you quickly regain your bearings.
  MOVE ZYSTARRM
ENDIF  

IFVAR ORG ! 13
  IFVAR ZYCHECK = 0
    EQUAL ZYCHECK 1
    PLREVENT 10
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL The smoke dissipates.
    MOVEALL ZYSTARRM
    EQUAL ZYCHECK 0
  ENDIF
ENDIF

