  ECHO OTHERS %n doubles over at the waist, hacking and wheezing.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The smoke stings at your eyes and you are forced to snap them shut.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB PROJECT -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The smoke stings your eyes mercilessly, bungling any attempts at concentration.
ENDIF

IFSAY tnylkjsdfghj#$!
  ELSE
  ECHO PLAYER You begin to speak, inhale some of the choking smoke, and double over hacking and wheezing.
  ECHO OTHERS %n doubles over at the waist as %h attempts to speak in the smoke.
ENDIF
