NUMBER 671
NAME Crumbling Room
*DESCRIPTION_START
Once a small back room, this place has been reduced to rubble. Scorched holes
in the wall allow the fresh outside air to run across your face. You can see
out to the stairway once used by mugger Bob to deal his wares, also destroyed
in the explosion. Smatterings of blood are all that remain of the victims of
the explosion.
*DESCRIPTION_END
CALL 33
EXIT O 2032
