NUMBER 643
NAME Between Two Walls
*DESCRIPTION_START
You feel a twinge of claustrophobia as you slink into this tiny space and 
allow your gaze to wander about. Squeezed between two walls, you are forced 
to turn sideways in order to fit semi-comfortably. There is a hole cut in the 
floor with a ladder that descends into darkness below. A small door sits next 
to a narrow glass window.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_FLOOR
CALL 33
ASTRAL      
FIXED_LIGHT
ITEM 0 335 adj1=183 adj2=355 val2=599
 EXTEND 0 descending into darkness
ITEM 1 943 val1=5000 val2=598 val3=589 LOCKED
ITEM 2 475
IFPREVERB go 2 
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER You carefully open the window and climb out onto the rooftop.
 ECHO OTHERS %n pulls open the window and climbs out onto the rooftop.
 MOVE 642
 AFFECT 642
 ECHO OTHERS %n climbs out of a window and closes it behind %i.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 2
 CLEARVERB
 SHOWROOM 642
ENDIF
NUMBER 644
NAME Alley
*DESCRIPTION_START
The chittering of rats and the stench of dried urine fill your senses as you
move through the dark alleyway. Splinters and fragments of glass bottles crunch
beaneath your feet when you stop beside a giant stack of wooden crates,
apparently discarded here by one of the nearby establishments. The Poor Quarter
lays to the south.
*DESCRIPTION_END
DAY_LIGHT
CALL 33
ASTRAL
EXIT S 287
ITEM 0 1033
IFPREVERB LOOK 0
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER Stamped onto the end of each crate is the name, "Northland Winery"
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CLIMB 0
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER Taking a nervous breath, you scramble up the stack of crates.
 ECHO OTHERS %n scrambles up the stack of crates and disappears upon reaching the top.
 MOVE 642
 AFFECT 642
 ECHO OTHERS %n scrambles up onto the rooftop.
ENDIF
NUMBER 415
NAME Training Hall
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CALL 33
INDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
This room seems to serve two purposes. Various works of art and masterfully
crafted objects mingle with equipment fit for training the best of thieves.
The room itself is floored and walled with white marble, polished to reflect
your gaze nearly perfectly. Beautiful marble statues are strung with bells for
young thieves to practice filching without a sound. Locking mechanisms of 
varying difficulty are built into polished ironwood chests crafted by 
Kragenholms masters. A tunnel leaves to the south back to the rock chamber.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ASTRAL
EXIT S 630
IFPREVERB RESIGN -1
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER The trainer looks up and growls, "Only one way out and that's in a box. You're staying right there."
 ECHO OTHERS A trainer glares at %n and growls, "Only one way out and that's in a box. You're staying right there."
 GMMSG *** %n just tried to resign from the thieves guild. Someone email Shadows and tell Sean who, please! ***
ENDIF

